{"tid":224590,"cid":21,"subCid":0,"title":"許冠傑「同舟共濟」27年後還看今天 有幾多又真係兌現到呢","createTime":"2017-05-01T07:30:10.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-06T03:38:48.000Z","uid":28802,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"75c20ed413649d2bb66d204b5b04b61f56121ed1","tid":224590,"uid":28802,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-01T07:30:10.000Z","msg":"我與你同坐這條船，無情浪把它猛捲，滿天風雨，<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">視野未能見，亂作一大團，不知怎算</span>。（sad but true<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> )<br />\n既決意留在這條船，齊齊令它不遭破損，困境挑戰，<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">奮勇地面對，令到這條船，永不翻轉</span>。<br />\n<br />\n香港是我心，一顆不變心，<span style=\"color: red;\">實在極不願，移民外國做二等公民</span>，<br />\n必須抱著信心，把基礎打穩，盡力地做我本份，定能突破戰勝黑暗。<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n破鏡明日定會重圓，<span style=\"color: blue;\">時局定必得好轉</span>，懷著希冀，<br />\n再創造時勢，令到這條船，永久溫暖。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">香港是我家，怎捨得失去它，實在極不願，移民外國做遞菜斟茶，</span><br />\n緊緊抱著結他，傾出這心裏話，但藉著這番話，齊齊共你發洩一下，<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">但願日後獅子山下，人人團結，永不分化</span>。<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n記得以前細個成日會聽到呢首歌，覺得香港係一個好好嘅地方，今日無意中聽番意見完全唔同曬<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 以前香港人正面嘅思維終究不服，由上年周國賢嘅「今生不回家」，寫出港人對香港前途嘅迷茫絕望，非不得要離開呢個熟悉嘅都巿，去異鄉做二等公民，同1990年大家仍然盼望有同舟共濟嘅精神成好大對比，許冠傑藉呢首「同舟共濟」去反映香港人當時對97回歸傍惶不安港人嘅心聲，希望勉勵當時嘅香港市民要對未來有信心，但可惜亦敵不過一次大型嘅移民潮.<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n同舟共濟 --- 許冠傑 (43:20-47:14) (1990香港心連心「凝聚每分光」演唱會）<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/7xLwiKzIbX8\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F7xLwiKzIbX8&d=Z58AETknIeTPCCdXMCOVUy7PofNJLCAwyGXsi6MH%2FEQ%3D&h=a02610b0\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/7xLwiKzIbX8</a><br />\n<br />\n今生不回家 --- 周國賢MV (2016)<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/jqzQq28QUAc\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FjqzQq28QUAc&d=Z58AETknIeTPCCdXMCOVUy7PofNJLCAwyGXsi6MH%2FEQ%3D&h=fec03e33\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/jqzQq28QUAc</a>"},{"pid":"d7d0a68fa50a4c72b66d6cf808134ecedb3aa518","tid":224590,"uid":28802,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-01T07:30:43.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c0f3f18506e8598ae7fbfc85b1748ac15b9345f4","tid":224590,"uid":28802,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-01T07:31:56.000Z","msg":"希望路過會望下啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"905b2368452a3ffa2641f7e8b3e6cd9013b118e6","tid":224590,"uid":28802,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-01T07:34:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/fozen_smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/lomore_hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3c2a8a5b1305997d8e2dddd823dfe3d50e832c33","tid":224590,"uid":90863,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-01T07:36:17.000Z","msg":"唱個個人都移左民<br />\n你話呢"},{"pid":"1a8426d162413905c4780b97becdb9d99f667b48","tid":224590,"uid":28802,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-01T07:41:09.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>唱個個人都移左民<br />\n你話呢</blockquote><br />\nSam Hui有咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d0d74ae23e6ec7d41b201eb3a352f53903384559","tid":224590,"uid":28802,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-01T07:42:15.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>唱個個人都移左民<br />\n你話呢</blockquote><br />\nHui Kwun Kit<br />\n英文名\tSam（Samuel）Hui<br />\n暱稱\t大哥Sam、歌神<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">國籍\t香港 中國（香港）</span><br />\n籍貫\t廣東番禺<br />\n出生\t1948年9月6日（68歲）<br />\n中華民國 中華民國廣東省廣州市<br />\n職業\t音樂人、歌手、詞曲作家、唱片製作人、演員<br />\n語言\t粵語、英語<br />\n教育程度\t香港大學心理學系學士畢業<br />\n母校\t聖芳濟書院<br />\n英華書院<br />\n宗教信仰\t天主教<br />\n配偶\tRebecca Hui（1972年結婚）<br />\n兒女\t許懷欣<br />\n- 1976年9月3日（40歲）<br />\n許懷谷<br />\n- 1978年2月14日（39歲）"},{"pid":"cddf37ae085c529a28538dc1ea3733fc090238