62fd47b3e04c177adcfbddc55f9d9f3b988daac6","tid":224590,"uid":13544,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-01T15:53:42.000Z","msg":"仲有三子之母陳美齡 唱香港香港 跟住走咗去日本<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/02.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"204c3f468e91031cca87c4da23e191a63fbd5e3d","tid":224590,"uid":62815,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-01T15:57:15.000Z","msg":"條粉腸一個屈尾十走咗去啦<br />\n香港精神閃避卸就有佢份<br />\n復出R光環cap水又係一絕<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4bc75e19ea28ab1b5c2e756543fd00bbaf9f60f3","tid":224590,"uid":28802,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-01T15:58:51.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>1990年 許冠傑《同舟共濟》、《話知你97》等作品同香港人講唔使驚<br />\n<br />\n1992年2月23日 《許冠傑光榮引退匯群星》係TVB播出，作為佢移民加拿大前既最後派對<br />\n<br />\n所以每次聽到呢幾隻歌我都覺得好諷刺，就好似而家成班高官叫你北望神州，有起咩事上黎就有哂盤算，話走就走。</blockquote><br />\n佢有走架原來<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3498f9aaf5691d47f5a3a8dcc9250181e2871f68","tid":224590,"uid":28802,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-01T15:59:31.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>條粉腸一個屈尾十走咗去啦<br />\n香港精神閃避卸就有佢份<br />\n復出R光環cap水又係一絕<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n隔2,3年就開演唱會<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2d7869e2b874495c69ff7e3558a2b7ee5db5fa95","tid":224590,"uid":81372,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-09T13:32:17.000Z","msg":"許冠傑在2016年《請✓許冠傑演唱會》台上強調從來沒有移民，一直住在香港。"},{"pid":"287e93e327d98b73db761160cdca84b0c05a122e","tid":224590,"uid":81372,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-10T02:13:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dc702fda086acb90f355a1e7e84aa4132cf7648d","tid":224590,"uid":81372,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-06T03:38:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}